      "summary": "Kunekune (くねくね) is a modern Japanese urban legend that emerged in the late 1990s through early internet forums and message boards.",
      "full": "Kunekune (くねくね) is a modern Japanese urban legend that emerged in the late 1990s through early internet forums and message boards. The name derives from the Japanese onomatopoeia \\\"kunekune,\\\" meaning \\\"wriggling\\\" or \\\"writhing,\\\" which describes its characteristic undulating movement. Unlike traditional yokai rooted in centuries of folklore, kunekune represents a new generation of horror: a purely internet-born entity that taps into primal human fears while incorporating modern anxieties about perception, distance, and incomprehensible phenomena."
    },
